    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Protective floor coverings, such as those made of a coarse material intended to protect the floor, or those made as a resilient or padded covering to protect athletes during practice or performance.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
